Demaste is tagged in League of Honour.  A good/neutral guild (neutrals with good tendencies).  (As a matter of fact, he's still listed in our roster, but I havent' seen him around. Not sure where he's been.  If he's asked to join Harvesters, I gotta check whether he's disbanded.)  He's always roleplayed a rather nutty neutral, with evil friends (Sarhea) but preferring the company of good aligned folks.  <br>
<br>
With that in mind, I can understand Inthul's objection.  But rather than telling folks IC that the guild is no longer evil only, I'd have a) waited to see whether they get tagged in the first place b) OOC informed the guild officers that you do not agree with their choice, before basically scaring folks away from the guild.<br>
