<br>
If the game did not have guidlines set by the alignments it would turn into a highly controversial and debated RP enviroment.  Making RP consistency a real chore to maintain.<br>
<br>
Look all over this forum at the RP debates, all are do to the people who want to step outside the alignment guidelines provided to us.  Without them we cannot hope to have an enviroment that is true for all in the community.  Having the limitations that this is just a game, I think we need the set alignments to allow for smooth RP and gameplay. <br>
